# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Uniform)

## Summary
Reverted to uniform sensitivity for all fingers.

## Configuration
- **Threshold**: `0.10` (All Fingers).
- **Smoothing**: Active (Alpha 0.7).

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
